title: The Ghosts Conspire | American Horror Stories - Episode 2: "Rubber (Wo)man - Part Two" (HD Clip)
author: AHS Crave
description:
Ruby (Kaia Gerber) tells Scarlett (Sierra McCormick) that Halloween is the only night of the year when ghosts are able to walk free. Unfortunately for them, Maya (Paris Jackson) & friends overheard the conversation...
